a.n: Jim Slip - Doncha Wanna Kiss Holly's Arse? with Holly Kiss

The girls with perfect makeup and their hair tied back neatly, looking like butter wouldn't melt in their mouthes.....you just want to ravage them!! Anyway, Holly was perfect for this whole haughty, look. I reckon I might have to one day get Holly and Lara to dress up in identical outfits and take one of their many male fans to task, with their riding crops and boots, so watch this space!
